text.tspan: Share of direct primary energy consumption by source, World
Primary energy is calculated using the 'direct method' which does not take account of the inefficiencies in energy production from fossil fuels.
Data source: Our World in Data based on BP Statistical Review of World Energy (2022)
Note: 'Other renewables' includes bioenergy, geothermal, wave, and tidal. It does not include traditional biofuels.
